Paula Abdul, 60, showed off her impressive agelessness in a new Instagram post that flaunted her youthful complexion. The Opposites Attract singer took to the social media platform to unveil her latest project in view of her 502,000 followers. Paula could be seen in the short clip smiling from ear to ear as she waved at the camera before introducing her new sunglasses brand, IdolEyes. The pop star, who appeared to be filming in her Las Vegas accommodation, donned a baby pink mini blazer dress that put her toned legs on display. Paula added some matte black tights and black shoes to the look, which she accessorised with a pearl necklace.